                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <h3 class="phase-title">Nutritional Rehabilitation</h3>
                        <p>Gradual introduction of nutrient-dense foods, focusing on proteins, vitamins, and minerals that address specific deficiencies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
